of Governour <HI>blake,</HI> Mr. <HI>James Moore</HI> procur'd him&s;elf to be elected
Governour in his room, by divers indirect and illegal Practices. This E|lection
is made by the Council, which is compos'd of the Proprietors
Deputys: And they are the Heads of that Faction from which all the
M$$erys of this Province chiefly proceed. They appear'd extreme|ly
