cou'd once exclude them the Commons Hou&s;e of A&s;&s;embly, they
&s;hou'd never be in Danger of being call'd to account, for $word$
thus the Con&s;titution of the Proviace in all its Paris, to their own
A varice and Ambition; becau&s;e there is not a &s;ufficient number of
