the Dioce&s;s, and have &s;et up a High Commi&s;&s;ion Court, and given
them&s;elves a merely Eccle&s;ia&s;tical Cognizance,<NOTE PLACE="marg">See the case of the $word$ Mr. Mar&s;$on $ere|unto an|nexd, N$. 14.</NOTE> as it was notorious
they threatned they wou'd &s;ome time before they accompli&s;h'd their
De&s;ign. And a much larger Cognizance it is, and a much greater
