and of which this Province is a Part; and
that We, may avoid erecting a numerous
<HI>Democracy,</HI> we the <HI>Lords</HI> and <HI>Proprietors</HI>
of the Province afore&s;aid, have agreed to
this following Form of <HI>Government,</HI> to be
perpetually e&s;tabli&s;hed among&s;t us, unto
which we do oblige our &s;elves, our Heirs
and Succe&s;&s;ors, in the mo&s;t binding Ways
