<P>&sect;. 1. THE <HI>Elde&s;t</HI> of the <HI>Lords Pre|prietors</HI>
&s;hall be <HI>Palatine,</HI> and
upon the Decea&s;e of the <HI>Palatine,</HI> the
<HI>Elde&s;t</HI> of the Seven &s;urviving <HI>Proprietors</HI>
&s;hall always &s;ucceed him.</P>
<P>&sect;. 2. There &s;hall be <HI>Seven</HI> other <HI>Chief
