but one, after &s;uch Vacancy, &s;hall have
Power to <HI>chu&s;e</HI> any <HI>Landgrave</HI> to be <HI>Pro|prietor.</HI></P>
<P><PB N="13" REF="54">
&sect;. 7. Who&s;oever after the Year One
